gantt
    title Software Project
    dateFormat YYYY-MM-DD
    axisFormat %m/%d
    excludes weekends
    section Planning
    Requirements: done, req, 2024-01-01, 2024-01-05
    Design: done, des, after req, 5d
    section Development
    Backend: active, be, after des, 10d
    Frontend: fe, after des, 10d
    section Release
    Testing: crit, test, after be, 5d
    Launch: milestone, launch, after test, 0d
repo_description: Parse and render Mermaid diagrams to/from AST
